  "text": "However, the collection of saliva for the profiling of DNA methylation holds promise [CITATION_1] , with methylation sites in saliva concordant with methylation within the target tissue for some specific biomarkers. To our knowledge, this has yet to be explored within an exercise setting but, if salivary DNA methylation profiling for exercise-related modifications becomes feasible, it will remove a substantial barrier to entry for methylation profiling within elite sport.",
